<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="C" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Courtier" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Courtier,</orth> 1) one who attends or frequents the courts of princes: <bibl n="shak. wiv 2.2.62" default="NO" valid="yes">Wiv. II, 2, 62</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. wiv 3.2.8" default="NO" valid="yes">III, 2, 8</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. lll 1.2.65" default="NO" valid="yes">LLL I, 2, 65</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. ayl 2.7.36" default="NO" valid="yes">As II, 7, 36</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. ayl 3.2.51" default="NO" valid="yes">III, 2, 51</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. ayl 4.1.12" default="NO" valid="yes">IV, 1, 12</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. ayl 5.4.42" default="NO" valid="yes">V, 4, 42</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. ayl 5.4.42" default="NO" valid="yes">V, 4, 42</bibl> <bibl n="shak. aww 1.1.80" default="NO" valid="yes">All's I, 1, 80</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tn 3.1.97" default="NO" valid="yes">Tw. III, 1, 97</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 2h6 4.4.36" default="NO" valid="yes">H6B IV, 4, 36</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. h8 1.3.22" default="NO" valid="yes">H8 I, 3, 22</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tro 1.3.234" default="NO" valid="yes">Troil. I, 3, 234</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. rom 1.4.72" default="NO" valid="yes">Rom. I, 4, 72</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tim 4.3.241" default="NO" valid="yes">Tim. IV, 3, 241</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. ham 1.2.117" default="NO" valid="yes">Hml. I, 2, 117</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. ham 3.1.159" default="NO" valid="yes">III, 1, 159</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. ham 5.1.90" default="NO" valid="yes">V, 1, 90</bibl> etc.<lb />Feminine: <bibl n="shak. wiv 3.3.66" default="NO" valid="yes">Wiv. III, 3, 66</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. aww 1.1.169" default="NO" valid="yes">All's I, 1, 169</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. h8 2.3.83" default="NO" valid="yes">H8 II, 3, 83</bibl>.
<lb />2) courter, wooer: <cit><quote>--s of beauteous freedom,</quote> <bibl n="shak. ant 2.6.17" default="NO" valid="yes">Ant. II, 6, 17</bibl></cit>.
